(4,4,'<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">首先小编先来回答大家关于2020年二级建造师考试准考证打印错过时间了怎么办?这个问题，如果时间错过了，没有打印准考证，考生是无法参加考试的，所以只能再等一年重新报名参加考试，所以在这里提醒大家一定要关注打印准考证时间，在规定的时间内打印准考证。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><strong>2020年全国二级建造师准考证打印常见问题</strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\"><strong>问题一: 准考证打印照片有颜色要求吗?</strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">回答：二级建造师准考证打印颜色上没有硬性要求，考生准考证一般采用黑白打印，只要用A4纸打印出来信息清新可见即可。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\"><strong>问题二：准考证遗失怎么办?</strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">回答：准考证丢了可以再打印，不过要在规定的时间内打印。建议打印的时候多打几份，这样丢了还有备份。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">温馨提示：二级建造师准考证是考生参加考试时间必须携带的东西之一，所以考生一定要保管好自己的准考证。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\"><strong>问题三：准考证打印忘记登录密码怎么办?</strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">回答：密码忘记了可以通过密码找回功能找回密码即可，实在找不回，可以电话咨询当地人事考试机构。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\"><strong>问题四：准考证打印信息不显示怎么办?</strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">回答：1、使用电脑自带的IE浏览器重新试一下</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">2、重新下载pdf文件阅读器查看。建议可下载系统页面提供免费下载pdf文件阅读器FoxitReader或到其它合法网站自行下载pdf阅读器。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\"><strong>问题五：准考证打印入口进不去怎么办?</strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">回答：部分地区报名考生较多，准考证打印期间系统繁忙，考生可以错过打印高峰期登录系统。另外，为了确保系统功能的正常使用，建议考生使用IE8.0及以上浏览器登录系统。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">如有其它问题，请及时咨询当地人事考试机构，避免错过打印时间。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">温馨提示：请各位考生务必在规定时间内打印准考证并保存好，以免影响考试。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\"><strong>问题六：准考证打印次数有限制吗?</strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">回答：没有限制，可以打印多份，但必须在规定时间内。打印准考证时，考生可多打印几张作为备用，准考证自行打印后，如果考生到考点后发现没带准考证，只要记得自己的登录号和密码，就可以就近到有电脑、打印机的地方自行打印。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\"><strong>问题七：准考证打印时没有反应怎么办?</strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">回答：1、造成这个原因有可能是打印准考证的人数众多，系统也比较慢，考生可以换个时间段打印。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">2、建议使用IE浏览器下载准考证，如果已经是IE浏览器，则请检查是否安装迅雷等下载软件，如果安装请暂时禁用或者卸载，使用IE自带下载功能下载打印准考证。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">3、直接用网页上的打印选项打印(注：打印选项在工具里面，如果是IE浏览器按Alt+Xj键即可。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">4、截图打印</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\"><strong>问题八：准考证打印照片不显示怎么办?</strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">回答：照片不显示的原因有可能是以下原因造成成的：</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">1、网速不稳定;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">2、打印官网、打印系统不稳定;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">3、浏览器问题。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">对于1、2点等网速稳定之后再试试看，实在不行可以电话咨询当地人事考试机构。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">对于第3点的解决办法如下：</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">①使用IE8.0及更高版本的浏览器;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">②点击右上角工具&mdash;Internet选项&mdash;高级，然后往下拉，找到打印选项之下有个打印图片，勾选上，点击确定，再重启浏览器，登录打印即可打印出照片了。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\"><strong>2020年二级建造师考试科目及时间</strong></p>','2020-10-21 14:53:05','2020-10-21 14:53:05',NULL),
