sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">D.限速器在联动试验中应使电梯主机延时制动</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">【参考答案】D</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">【参考解析】电梯整机验收的要求：</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(1) 当控制柜三相电源中任何一相断开或任何两相错接时，断相、错相保护装置或功能应使电梯不发生危险故障。当错相不影响电梯正常运行时可没有错相保护装置或功能。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(2) 动力电路、控制电路、安全电路必须有与负载匹配的短路保护装置;动力电路必须有过载保护装置。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(3) 限速器上的轿厢(对重、平衡重)下行标志必须与轿厢(对重、平衡重)的实际下行方向相符。限速器铭牌上的额定速度、动作速度必须与被检电梯相符。限速器必须与其型式试验证书相符。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sa