(7,7,'<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\"><strong>2020二级建造师建设工程施工管理知识点：施工现场环境污染的处理</strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">1.大气污染的处理</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(1)施工现场外围围挡不得低于1.8m，以避免或减少污染物向外扩散。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(2)施工现场垃圾杂物要及时清理。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(3)施工现场道路应硬化。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(4)易飞扬材料入库密闭存放或覆盖存放。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(5)施工现场易扬尘处使用密目式安全网封闭，使一网两用，并定人定时清洗粉尘，防止施工过程扬尘或二次污染。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(6)禁止施工现场焚烧有毒、有害烟尘和恶臭气体的物资。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(7)尾气排放超标的车辆，应安装净化消声器，防止噪声和冒黑烟。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(8)拆除旧有建筑物时，应适当洒水，并且在旧有建筑物周围采用密目式安全网和草帘搭设屏障，防止扬尘。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(9)在城区、郊区城镇和居民稠密区、风景旅游区、疗养区及国家规定的文物保护区内施工的过程，严禁使用敞口锅熬制沥青。凡进行沥青防水作业时，要使用密闭和带有烟尘处理装置的加热设备。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">2.水污染的处理</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(1)施工现场搅拌站的污水、水磨石的污水等须经排水沟排放和沉淀池沉淀后再排入城市污水管道或河流，污水未经处理不得直接排入城市污水管道或河流。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(2)禁止将有毒有害废弃物作土方回填，避免污染水源。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(3)施工现场存放油料、化学溶剂等设有专门的库房，必须对库房地面和高250mm墙面进行防渗处理，如采用防渗混凝土或刷防渗漏涂料等。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(4)施工现场100人以上的临时食堂，污水排放时可设置简易有效的隔油池，定期掏油、清理杂物，防止污染水体。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">3.噪声污染的处理</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(1)在人口密集区进行较强噪声施工时，须严格控制作业时间，一般避开晚10时到次日早6时的作业;对环境的污染不能控制在规定范围内的，必须昼夜连续施工时，要尽量采取措施降低噪声。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(2)夜间噪声最大声级超过限值的幅度不得高于15dB(A)建筑施工场界噪声限值：昼间控制在70dB(A)，夜间控制在55dB(A)</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">以上就是环球网校二级建造师频道为大家整理的关于2020年二级建造师《施工管理》重要知识点：施工现场环境污染的处理，希望对大家有所帮助，您也可以点击文末免费下载按钮，免费领取更多考试相关的精华资料和真题解析。</p>','2020-10-21 14:55:10','2020-10-21 14:55:10',NULL),
(8,8,'<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">【摘要】 2020年二级建造师考试将在10月31日至11月1日进行，为了帮助大家更好的复习，环球网校二级建造师频道为大家整理了各科目的一些常见考点汇总，今天要给大家分享的是，2020年二级建造师《工程法规》高频考点归纳。希望对大家有所帮助。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">一、专利权</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">1、保护对象：发明、实用新型、外观设计</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">2、权利期限：(1)发明：20年;(2)实用新型与外观设计：10年。(均自申请日起计算)</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">二、商标权</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">1、同其他知识产权不同，商标专用权的内容只包括财产权，商标设计者的人身权受著作权法保护。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">商标专用权包括使用权和禁止权两方面。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">商标专用权的保护对象是经过国家商标管理机关核准注册的商标。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">2、商标有效期为10年，自核准注册之日起算。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">三、著作权</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">1、著作权主体</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">单位作品：著作权完全归单位所有。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">职务作品：著作权由作者享有，但法人或者其他组织有权在其业务范围内优先使用。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">委托作品：合同未明确约定或者没有订立合同的，著作权属于受托人。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">2、著作权的保护期限：</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(1)作者的署名权、修改权、保护作品完整权不受限制;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(2)自然人：终生加死后50年;合同作品：最后一方死亡后50年</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">好了，以上就是环球网校二级建造师频道为大家整理的2020年二级建造师《工程法规》高频考点归纳：知识产权的常见种类，您还可以点击下方按钮，免费领取更多备考资料和考点精华。</p>','2020-10-21 14:55:44','2020-10-21 14:55:44',NULL),
(9,9,'<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">首先我们分析一下做题速度慢和准确率低的原因，才能对症下药。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">1、知识点不熟练，没有掌握熟练的解题技巧。对学过的知识点不够熟练，在平时学习中缺少做题训练，不知道这些知识点会出哪些类型的题目，不知道使用哪种解题方法来解题。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">2、还有一种原因就是经验不足，也就是说题目练习的量不够。看到题目比较陌生，需要思考很久。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">3、有拖延症。在生活中有拖延症的人，在做题时速度也慢。大脑懒得去思考，做题时就会拖拉，明明一分钟可以完成，偏偏拖到五分钟。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">上述问题相信大部分考生在备考时都存在，那么提高做题速度和准确率呢?</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">1、多做题练习</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">要想提高解题速度，就要从做题入手，但不是盲目去做，要有一定的规划。针对不同的题目采取不同的解题方法。还有在复习过程中，需要加大自己的练习量，历年真题、模拟题等都需要排入练习计划，适当练习，熟能生巧。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">2、掐时间做题</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">解决拖延症的办法，就是定时定量，做每一道题都要掐好时间，在平时的训练中改掉一些做题时的小毛病，多多训练自己的解题思维，有了一定的解题思维以后就要开始慢慢缩短解题时间，当习惯了之后，做题速度自然能够提升。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">3、多总结，提升做题准确率</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">我们做过的每一道题，都是一笔财富。之前整理的错题本上的题目需要再做一遍，加深印象，才能避免再犯同样的错误。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">以上就是环球网校二级建造师频道为大家整理的关于2020年二级建造师考试如何提高做题速度，大家可以点击文末免费下载按钮，免费领取更多考点精华，其中涉及了考前冲刺模拟题，历年的真题及答案解析，同时还有高频考点的总结及专业老师分享的知识点及技巧，相信会对您最后的冲刺有所帮助。</p>','2020-10-21 14:56:58','2020-10-21 14:56:58',NULL),
(10,10,'<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">【摘要】2020年二级建造师考试马上就要到了，最后的冲刺阶段，环球网校小编给大家整理了各科的考点汇总，今天要介绍的是2020年二级建造师考试《建筑工程》速记考点汇总，希望能帮助大家提高备考效率。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">1、建筑装饰装修施工过程中常见的荷载变动主要有：</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(1)在楼面上加铺任何材料属于对楼板增加了面荷载;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(2)在室内增加隔墙、封闭阳台属于增加的线荷载;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(3)在室内增加装饰性的柱子，特别是石柱，悬挂较大的吊灯，房间局部增加假山盆景 ，这些装修做法就是对结构增加了集中荷载。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">2、梁的正截面破坏形式与配筋率、混凝土强度等级、截面形式等有关，影响最大的是配筋率。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">3、影响斜截面破坏的因素：截面尺寸、混凝土强度等级、荷载形式、箍筋和弯起钢筋的含量等，其中影响较大的是配箍率。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">4、在钢结构设计文件中，应注明建筑结构设计使用年限、钢材牌号、连接材料的型号(或钢号)、设计所需的附加保证项目和所采用的规范。此外，还应注明所要求的焊缝形式、焊缝质量等级、端面刨平顶紧部位、钢结构防护要求及措施、对施工的要求。对抗震设防的钢结构，关键连接部位应注明其连接的细部构造、尺寸，同时注明在塑性耗能区采用钢材的最大允许屈服应力。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">5、有较高要求的抗震结构适用的钢筋牌号为：</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">带肋钢筋牌号后加E(例如：HRB400E，HRBF400E)。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">该类钢筋还应满足以下要求：</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(1)实测抗拉强度与实测屈服强度之比不小于1.25;(强屈比&ge;1.25)</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(2)实测屈服强度与规定的屈服强度标准值之比不大于1.30;(超屈比&le;1.3)</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(3)最大力下总伸长率&ge;9%。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">6、钢材的主要性能包括力学性能和工艺性能。其中力学性能包括：拉伸性能、冲击性能、疲劳性能。工艺性能包括：弯曲性能和焊接性能。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">7、六大常用水泥的初凝时间均不得短于45min，硅酸盐水泥的终凝时间不得长于6.5h，其他五类常用水泥的终凝时间不得长于10h。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">8、采用胶砂法来测定水泥的3d和28d的抗压强度和抗折强度，根据测定结果来确定该水泥的强度等级。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">9、影响混凝土拌合物和易性的主要因素包括：</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">单位体积用水量、砂率、组成材料的性质、时间和温度等。其中单位体积用水量是最主要的因素。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">10、影响混凝土强度的因素</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(1) 原材料方面：</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">①水泥强度与水灰比;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">②骨料的种类、质量和数量;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">③外加剂和掺合料;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(2) 生产工艺方面：</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">①搅拌与振捣;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">②养护的温度和湿度;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">③龄期。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">11、缓凝剂主要用于高温季节混凝土、大体积混凝土、泵送与滑模方法施工以及远距离运输的商品混凝土等，不宜用于日最低气温5&deg;C以下施工的混凝土，也不宜用于有早强要求的混凝土和蒸汽养护的混凝土。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">12、抗压强度和抗折强度：</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">以边长为70.7mm的立方体试件，在标准养护条件下，用标准方法测得28d龄期的抗压强度值。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(1)以3个试件测值的算术平均值作为该组试件的砂浆立方体试件抗压强度平均值，精确至0.1MPa;(正常取平均)</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(2)当三个测值的最大值或最小值中如有一个与中间值的差值超过中间值的15%时，则把最大值及最小值一并舍去，取中间值作为该组试件的抗压强度值;(一超取中)</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(3)当两个测值与中间值的差值均超过中间值的15%时，则该组试件的试验结果为无效。(两超作废)</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">13、花岗石构造致密、强度高、密度大、吸水率极低、质地坚硬、耐磨，为酸性石材。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">14、人造石按主要原材料分包括人造石实体面材、人造石石英石和人造石岗石等产品。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">15、木材的含水量用含水率表示，指木材的水分质量占木材质量的百分数。分为绝对含水率和相对含水率。影响木材物理力学性质和应用的最主要的含水率指标是平衡含水率和纤维饱和点。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">16、安全玻璃包括钢化玻璃、均质钢化玻璃、防火玻璃和夹层玻璃。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">17、钢化玻璃机械强度高，抗冲击性也很高，弹性比普通玻璃大得多，热稳定性好，在受急冷急热作用时，不易发生炸裂，碎后不易伤人。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">18、通过对钢化玻璃进行均质(第二次热处理工艺)处理，可以大大降低钢化玻璃的自爆率。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">19、阳光控制镀膜玻璃：</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">具有良好的隔热性能，可以避免暖房效应。具有单向透视性，故又称为单反玻璃。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">20、防水涂料分为JS聚合物水泥基防水涂料、聚氨醋防水涂料、水泥基渗透结晶型防水涂料等。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">21、影响保温材料导热系数的因素有：</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(1)材料的性质;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(2)表观密度与孔隙特征;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(3)湿度;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(4)温度;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(5)热流方向。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">22、钢尺量距是目前楼层测量放线最常用的距离测量方法。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">23、DS05型和DS1型水准仪称为精密水准仪，用于国家一、二等水准测量。DS3称为普通水准仪，用于国家三、四等水准测量。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">24、水准仪的主要功能：</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(1)测量两点间的高差;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(2)由控制点的已知高程来推算测点的高程;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(3)测量两点间的大致水平距离。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">25、经纬仪的主要功能：</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(1)进行水平角和竖直角测量;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(2)测出两点间的大致水平距离和高差;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(3)进行点位的竖向传递测量。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">26、全站仪：</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">同时测量角度和距离的仪器，在同一时间得到平距、 高差、点的坐标和高程。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">27、施工测量现场主要工作有，对已知长度的测设、已知角度的测设、建筑物细部点平面位置的测设、建筑物细部点高程位置及倾斜线的测设等。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">28、土方填筑与压实</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(1)填土应从场地最低处开始，由下而上整个宽度分层铺填。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(2)填方应在相对两侧或周围同时进行回填和夯实。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(3)填土应尽量采用同类土填筑，填方的密实度要求和质量指标通常以压实系数表示。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">29、防止或减少降水影响周围环境的技术措施</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(1)采用回灌技术。采用回灌井点时，回灌井点与降水井点的距离不宜小于6m。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(2)采用砂沟、砂井回灌。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(3)减缓降水速度。还可在邻近被保护建(构) 筑物一侧，将井点管间距加大，必要时甚至暂停抽水。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">30、基坑验槽程序：</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(1)在施工单位自检合格的基础上进行。施工单位确认自检合格后提出验收申请。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(2)由总监理工程师或建设单位项目负责人组织建设、监理、勘察、设计及施工单位的项目负责人、技术质量负责人，共同按设计要求和有关规定进行。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(3)基槽满足设计要求及有关规定后，相关方履行验收手续;需要局部处理的部位由设计单位提出处理意见，施工单位处理后进行二次验收。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">31、基坑验槽的主要内容</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(1)基槽平面位置、尺寸和深度是否符合设计要求。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(2)观察土质及地下水情况是否和勘察报告相符。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(3)检查基槽之中是否有旧建筑物基础、古井、古墓、洞穴、地下掩埋物及地下人防工程等。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(4)检查基槽边坡外缘与附近建筑物的距离，基坑开挖对建筑物稳定是否有影响。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(5)检查核实分析钎探资料，对存在有异常点位应进行复查。桩基应检测桩的质量是否合格。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">32、基坑验槽方法：</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(1)观察法(重点观察柱基、墙角、承重墙下或其他受力较大部位)</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(2)钎探法</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(3)轻型动力触探。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">33、遇有下列情况之一时，应进行轻型动力触探：</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(1)持力层明显不均匀;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(2)局部有软弱下卧层;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(3)有浅埋的坑穴、古墓、古井等，直接观察难以发现时;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(4)勘察报告或设计文件规定应进行轻型动力触探时。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">34、砖、石基础属于刚性基础范畴，抗压性能好，整体性、抗拉、抗弯、抗剪性能较差。适用于地基坚实、均匀，上部荷载较小，7层和7层以下的一般民用建筑和墙承重的轻型厂房基础工程。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">35、砖基础施工技术要求</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(1)砖基础大放脚一般采用一顺一丁砌筑形式，上下皮垂直灰缝相互错开60mm。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(2)砖基础的水平灰缝厚度和垂直灰缝宽度宜为10mm。水平灰缝的砂浆饱满度不得小于80%，竖向灰缝的砂浆饱满度不得小于90%。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(3)砖基础底标高不同时，应从低处砌起，并应由高处向低处搭砌。搭砌长度不应小于砖基础底的高差。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(4)砖基础的转角处和交接处应同时砌筑，当不能同时砌筑时，应留置斜槎。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(5)基础墙的防潮层位置宜在室内地面标高以下一皮砖处。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">36、大体积混凝土的振捣：</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(1)混凝土应采取振捣棒振捣。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(2)在初凝以前对混凝土进行二次振捣，排除混凝土因泌水在粗骨料、水平钢筋下部生成的水分和空隙，提高混凝土与钢筋的握裹力;防止因混凝土沉落而出现的裂缝，减少内部微裂;增加混凝土密实度，使混凝土抗压强度提升，从而提高抗裂性。</p>','2020-10-21 15:01:38','2020-10-21 15:01:38',NULL),
(11,11,'<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">【摘要】2020年二级建造师考试马上就要到了，最后的冲刺阶段，环球网校小编给大家整理了各科的考点汇总，今天要介绍的是二级建造师《水利水电工程》考点归纳，希望能帮助大家提高备考效率。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">1.按坝高分类:中坝：30m&le;h&le;70m(对所有坝都适用)【提醒：易考选择题】</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">2.Ⅳ级以下的坝下游也可以采用草皮护面。【提醒：易考选择题】</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">3.防浪墙的高度一般为 1.0～1.2m 。【提醒：易考选择/案例】</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">4.防渗体的作用：①减少通过坝体和坝基的渗流量;②降低浸润线，增加下游坝坡的稳定性;③降低渗透坡降，防止渗透变形。【有可能考案例，也有可能给你一个图，让你判断属于什么部位，以及作用?】</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">5.土石坝的护坡的作用：①防止波浪淘刷②顺坝水流冲刷③冰冻④其他形式的破坏。【提醒：易考选择/案例】</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">6.坝体排水(排内部渗水)形式有：贴坡排水、棱体排水、褥垫排水、管式排水、综合式排水。【提醒：易考选择题】</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">7.贴坡排水作用：①将渗入坝体内的水有计划的排出坝外。②以达到降低坝体孔隙水压力，防止坝坡土冻胀破坏。注意贴坡排水属于特殊项(不能降低浸润线)【提醒：有可能给你一个图，让你判断属于什么部位，以及作用?】</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">8.扬压力包括【注意对比】</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(1)Ps 是指渗透压力 上、下游水位差</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(2)PF是指上浮力下游水深</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">9.下游连接段包括护坦(消力池)、海漫、下游防冲槽以及下游翼墙与护坡等。【提醒：易考多选】</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">10.海漫构造要求：①表面粗糙，能够沿程消除余能;②透水性好，以利渗流顺利排出;③具有一定的柔性，能够适应河床变形。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">11.总结【注意对比】</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(1)上游连接段：由铺盖、护底、护坡及上游翼墙组成。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(2)闸室：包括底板、闸墩、闸门、胸墙、工作桥和交通桥等。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(3)下游连接段：包括护坦(消力池)、海漫、下游防冲槽以及下游翼墙与护坡等。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">12.橡胶坝分袋式(常用)、帆式及钢柔混合结构式三种坝型。【提醒：易考选择题】</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">13.叶片泵分类：离心泵、轴流泵、混流泵。【提醒：易考选择题】</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">14.离心泵启动前 泵壳和进水管内必须充满水。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">15.轴流泵抽水装置：无需充水设备。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">16.水泵铭牌上标出的扬程，是泵的设计扬程(又称额定扬程)</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">17.水泵能量损失：分水力、容积和机械损失。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">18.移动式：分为囤船型和缆车型。【能动的】</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">19.渠系建筑物的构造及作用 在渠道上修建的水工建筑物类型主要有渡槽、涵洞、倒虹吸管、跌水与陡坡等。(注意:没有堤防)【提醒：易考选择题】</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">20.沉降缝主要作用是适应地基的不均匀沉降。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">21.截水环用以防止洞身外围产生集中渗流。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">22.水库工程中最大高度超过 200m 的大坝建筑物,其级别应为 1 级。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">23.临时性水工建筑物级别根据：保护对象+失事后果+使用年限+临时性挡水建筑物规模;【提醒：易考选择/案例】</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">24.按基本构造形态分：【注意区分】</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(1)产状：走向、倾向和倾角等;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(2)褶皱：背斜和向斜;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(3)断裂：正断层、逆断层、平移断层(提醒：易考选择题，给你一个图让判断属于哪一种形式)</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">25.边坡变形：松弛张裂、蠕变、崩塌、滑坡。【提醒：注意与渗透变形相区分】</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">26.渗透变形：管涌、流土、接触冲刷、接触流失。【提醒：注意与上相区分】</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">27.防止边坡失稳的措施：设置合理坡度、边坡护面、基坑支护、降低地下水位等。【案例题】</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">28.水准仪分类及作用中：DS3 代表： D 为&ldquo;大地测量&rdquo;,S&ldquo;水准仪&rdquo;，3 表示每公里往返测量高差中数的偶然中误差为&plusmn;3mm。【提醒：易考选择题】</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">29.测量误差来源：仪器误差、观测误差(主要来源)和外界条件影响。【提醒：易考选择题】</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">30.经纬仪 DJ05 代表：如\"05\" 表示一测回方向观测中误差不超过土 0.5\"。【提醒：易考选择题】</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">31.根据度盘刻度和读数方式分：游标经纬仪、光学经纬仪和电子经纬仪。【提醒：易考选择题】</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">32.测量误差分类【注意区分】【提醒：易考选择题】</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(1)系统误差：有规律。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(2)偶然误差：没有规律。主要是由于人的感觉器官和仪器的性能限制。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">(3)粗差：可避免。观测者粗心或者受到干扰造成。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">33.对于高程放样中误差应不大于 10mm 的部位应采用水准测量法(精度要求高)【提醒：易考选择题】</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">34.用渗透系数 K 表示，K 值越大，表示其抗渗性能越差;如材料的抗渗等级为 W4、W1O,分别表示试件抵抗静水水压力的能力为 0.4MPa 和 1MPa。【W 值越大，表示其抗渗性能越强】【案例题】</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">35.用抗冻等级 F 表示，如 F25、F50,分别表示材料抵抗 25 次、50 次冻融循环，而强度损失未超过 25%，质量损失未超过 5%。【案例题】</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 32px; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', -apple-system, \'Noto Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Nimbus Sans L\', Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Noto Sans CJK SC\', \'Source Han Sans SC\', \'Source Han Sans CN\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Wenquanyi Micro Hei\', \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei\', \'ST Heiti\', SimHei, \'WenQuanYi Zen Hei Sharp\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 25px; word-break: break-all; color: #171920; background-color: #ffffff;\">36.用细度模数表示砂的粗细程度。MX越大，表示砂越粗。MX 在 3.0〜2.3 之间为中砂。 【提醒：易考选择题】</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-varian